(21, 1, 4, 'set-your-learning-objectives', 'y', 'webpage', '{embed="structure/header" use_my_placement_css=''yes''}\n\n		\n<h2>Set your Learning Objectives</h2>\n<div class="contrast">\n<ol>\n<li>Here you can set your learning objectives for this practice placement cycle.</li>\n<li class=''storedSteps''>You have not chosen steps for this cycle.</li>\n<li>Check your {summary_page_link} to reflect on your current strengths, skills, growth, knowledge and any gaps to help you write your \nlearning objectives for this practice placement.</li>\n</ol>\n<img src="/img/behind_the_scenes_vid2.png" style="text-align: left; width: 410px; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; float: right;">\n<p>The competency statements below have been generated from the {evidencing-matrix-link} and are reflective\nof the steps you chose in {prepare-for-practice-part2-link}:  <span class=''steps''></span> These competency statements also show the PRACSOT performance criteria\nto which they are related.</p>\n\n<p>The learning objectives you write and the information auto-generated from the {evidencing-matrix-link} will form your Learning Contract.  Your Learning Contract will automatically generate an updated version \nlater on during the practice placement cycle once you evidence your competence showing your evidence against your learning objectives.</p>\n\n<label for="objectives">My learning objectives:</label>\n<p>{how-to-write-learning-objectives-link}</p>\n<p id="objectives"><img src="/img/close-icon-white.png" class="exit"><textarea></textarea><img src=''/img/plus-icon.png'' class=''add''></img><br><img src=/img/ajax-loader-circle.gif class=loader></img></p>\n<br>\n\n<p><a href="/practice-placement/learning-contract-with-objectives" class="button" id="continue">Save &amp; Continue to View your learning contract →</a><br><br>\n<em style=''float:right''>All saved content will be saved to <a href="/practice-placement/summary-of-your-competencies">Your ePortfolio</a></em></p>\n</div>\n<div id=''otpp'' style=''display:none''> \n<div id=''exit-button''></div>\n    <object width="650" height="650" id="wheel" type="image/svg+xml" style="float:right; clear:right;" data="/svg/wheel.svg">\n  </object>\n</div>\n<div id=''criteria-data'' style=''display:none''></div>\n\n\n{embed="structure/footer" login_required=''true'' js_file=''level-defs-window.js''}\n{exp:practice_placement:set_your_learning_objectivesjs allowed_group_ids=''5'' no_access_message=''This functionality is only available to Student members.''}', '', 1379483787, 1, 'n', 0, '', 'n', 'n', 'o', 4474),
(47, 1, 4, 'learning-contract-with-objectives', 'y', 'webpage', '{embed="structure/header" use_my_placement_css=''yes''}\n<h2>Your Learning Contract with Learning Objectives</h2>\n<div class="contrast">\n<p>As you can see, your learning objectives have been added to the table below.</p>  \n<div id=''learning-contract-pane''>\n\n</div>\n<p><a id="continue" class="button" href="/practice-placement/plan-for-your-placement">Plan for your placement &rarr;</a></p>\n</div>\n<div id=''criteria-data'' style=''display:none''></div>\n\n{embed="structure/footer" login_required=''true''}\n\n{exp:practice_placement:learning_contractjs \nallowed_group_ids=''5'' \nno_access_message=''This functionality is only available to Student members.'' \njquery_selector=''#learning-contract-pane''\nplanning = ''false''\nevidence = ''false''\nobjectives = ''true''	\n}', '', 1380671929, 1, 'n', 0, '23', 'n', 'n', 'o', 1534),
