(40, 1, 8, 'user-status', 'y', 'webpage', '<?php\n/*\nExpressionEngine \nuser-status.html template\n\nURI:  /ajax/user-status/\n\nAn ajax template, POST a JSON object to this script to persist the current practice cycle.\nThe profile consists of user reflections and general settings for the practice cycle.  \nReflections (javascript: userProfile.reflections[]) are persisted in the otca_diary mySQL table.\nThe user status (javascript: userProfile.steps, userProfile.level, userProfile.beginner, userProfile.objectives) \nare persisted to the otca_user_status mySQL table.\n*/\n\n$member_id = $this->EE->session->userdata(''member_id'');\n\nif(!isset($member_id) || $member_id == 0) return;\n\n$userProfileInput = $this->EE->input->post(''userProfile'');\n\nif($userProfileInput) {\n	$userProfile = json_decode($userProfileInput);\n	if($userProfile->startNewCycle == ''true'') $endCycle = TRUE;\n	else $endCycle = FALSE;\n	\n		$steps = isset($userProfile->steps)?mysql_real_escape_string(json_encode($userProfile->steps)):'''';\n		$level = isset($userProfile->level)?$userProfile->level:0;\n		$beginner = isset($userProfile->beginner)?$userProfile->beginner:0;\n		$objectives = isset($userProfile->objectives)?mysql_real_escape_string(json_encode($userProfile->objectives)):"[]";\n		$title = isset($userProfile->title)?mysql_real_escape_string($userProfile->title):"";\n	\n	// create blank history item ready for saving this in the history later on... and so we can get the history_id	\n	if($userProfile->history_id == 0) {\n			$query = $this->EE->db->query("INSERT INTO `otca_user_status_history` (`member_id`, `steps`, `level`, `beginner`,`objectives`, `title`, `time`) VALUES (''$member_id'',''$steps'',''$level'',''$beginner'',''$objectives'', ''$title'', UNIX_TIMESTAMP() );");\n			$userProfile->history_id = $this->EE->db->insert_id(); \n	 }\n	$history_id = $userProfile->history_id;\n	foreach($userProfile->reflections as &$entry) {\n	   $text = mysql_real_escape_string($entry->text);\n          \n	   $timestamp = $entry->date;	\n	   $entry_id = isset($entry->internalId)?$entry->internalId:0;	\n	   $tag = isset($entry->tag)?$entry->tag:'''';\n            \n          // echo "$text >>>> $tag \\n\\n"; \n            \n          if(!empty($text) && !empty($tag)) {\n		if($entry_id != 0) {\n			$query =  $this->EE->db->query("UPDATE `otca_diary` SET `entry_text`=''$text'', `last_updated`=''$timestamp'' WHERE `member_id`=''$member_id'' AND `entry_id`=''$entry_id'' AND `tag` = ''$tag''"); \n		} else {		\n			$query =  $this->EE->db->query("INSERT INTO `otca_diary` (`member_id`,`entry_text`,`creation_date`, `current_practice_cycle`, `tag`) VALUES (''$member_id'',''$text'',''$timestamp'',''$history_id'', ''$tag'')");\n		}\n           }\n	}\n// save status\n$query = $this->EE->db->query("INSERT INTO `otca_user_status` (`member_id`, `steps`, `level`, `beginner`,`objectives`,`title`, `history_id`)\n                            VALUES (''$member_id'',''$steps'',''$level'',''$beginner'',''$objectives'', ''$title'', ''$history_id'')\n                            ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `steps`=''$steps'', `level`=''$level'', `beginner`=''$beginner'', `objectives`=''$objectives'',\n                            `title`=''$title'', `history_id`=''$history_id''");\n\n// update history\n$this->EE->db->query("UPDATE otca_user_status_history a, otca_user_status b SET a.steps = b.steps, a.level = b.level, a.beginner = b.beginner,a.objectives = b.objectives, a.title = b.title WHERE a.id = b.history_id AND a.member_id = ''$member_id''");\n\necho json_encode($userProfile->history_id);\n}	\n?>', '', 1380671929, 1, 'n', 0, '', 'n', 'y', 'i', 5179),
(70, 1, 3, 'core_javascript', 'y', 'webpage', '<script>\n$(document).ready(function() {\n	$.checkHistoryID = function(callback, noCallbackIfUserLoggedIn) {\n	if(typeof noCallbackIfUserLoggedIn == ''undefined'') noCallbackIfUserLoggedIn = false;\n		\n	if(typeof window.userProfile !== ''undefined'') {\n		if(window.userProfile.history_id == 0) {\n			$(''div#dialog-box > span#content'').append("<h2>Start a new Practice Placement Cycle</h2>\\\n								  <p>You start a new Practice Placement Cycle on this website whenever you start a new placement.</p>\\\n								  <p>You are now starting a new practice placement cycle, you will need to name it before continuing.\\\n								  This will save it to your profile for future use.</p><p>You can restore previous cycles from the toolbar\\\n								  at any time by clicking\\\n								  ''Manage Practice Placement Cycles'' and selecting the relevant cycle.</p><p>We recommend that you save\\\n								  your current cycle with a meaningful name.\\\n								  </p><label for=''cycle_name''><strong>Cycle name:</strong></label>\\\n								  <input name=''cycle_name'' type=''text'' />\\\n								  <button name=''save''>Save</button>");\n			$(''div#dialog-box'').show(100);\n		\n		var process = function(e) {\n			\n				// hack for IE 9 bug where this is added twice					\n				if($(''#dialog-box'').length > 1) {\n					$(''#dialog-box'').last().remove();\n					console.log("removed duplicate file-viewer DIV");\n				}\n				\n				var cycle_name = $("#dialog-box input[name=''cycle_name'']").val();\n				\n				if(typeof cycle_name !== ''undefined'' && cycle_name.length > 0) {\n						window.userProfile.title = cycle_name;\n						$(''#ajax-loader'').show();\n						$.post(''/ajax/user-status'', \n							{ "userProfile" : JSON.stringify(window.userProfile) }, \n							function(data) {\n								$(''#ajax-loader'').hide();\n								window.userProfile.history_id = data.history_id;\n								callback(cycle_name);\n							} \n							,''json'');\n				} else {\